October 13, 2015 PolitiFact live blog: Fact-checking the Democratic debate 
Welcome to PolitiFact's live coverage of the Democratic presidential debate. Coverage will begin at 8:30 p.m. Podiums stand on stage during a walk-through ahead of the first Democratic presidential debate at the Wynn Las Vegas resort and casino in Las Vegas, Nevada, U.S. on Tuesday, Oct. 13, 2015.
